<p class="about">
About City Compass<br>

City Compass is your ultimate digital guide to discovering the true essence of any city. 
Whether you're a traveler, a foodie, or a shopping enthusiast, we help you explore the most famous places, 
vibrant food streets, and buzzing shopping hubs, all in one place.<br>

Our goal is simple:<br>
To make city exploration easy, exciting, and authentic.<br>

From iconic landmarks to hidden local gems, City Compass provides curated recommendations that 
help you experience a city like a local. We bring together must-visit attractions, street food hotspots, popular markets, 
and cultural highlights so you never miss out on what makes a city special.<br><br>

What We Offer: <br>

Famous tourist attractions <br>
Popular food streets & local eateries <br>
Best shopping markets & malls<br>
Whether you’re planning a trip or just exploring your own city, City Compass points you in the right direction.<br>
Explore More. Taste More. Discover More.<br>
</p>


